56 void CartesianPositionController::readEndEffectorPosition() {
57  while (ros::ok()) {
58  try {
59  transform_listener.lookupTransform("/world", "/end_effector",
60  ros::Time(0), transform);
61  endEffectorPositionVector << transform.getOrigin().getX(),
62  transform.getOrigin().getY(),
63  transform.getOrigin().getZ();
64  break;
65  } catch (tf::TransformException ex) {
66  ros::Duration(0.3).sleep();
67  }
68  }
69 }

75 Eigen::VectorXd CartesianPositionController::secondaryTaskFunctionGradient(Eigen::VectorXd q) {
76  return 2.0/7.0 * (q - jointMiddleValues).cwiseQuotient(jointRanges);
77 }

79 Eigen::VectorXd CartesianPositionController::EEVelocityToQDot(Eigen::Vector3d desiredEEVelocity) {
80  J = kdlSolver.computeJacobian(std::string("end_effector"), q); J = J.block(0, 0, 3, 7);
81  Jpinv = J.completeOrthogonalDecomposition().pseudoInverse();
82  return Jpinv * desiredEEVelocity - secondaryTaskGain * ((Eigen::MatrixXd::Identity(7, 7) - Jpinv*J) * secondaryTaskFunctionGradient(q));
83 }

89 void CartesianPositionController::moveToPosition(const Eigen::Vector3d desiredPositionVector) {
90  positionErrorVector = desiredPositionVector - endEffectorPositionVector;
91 
92  while (positionErrorVector.norm() > position_error_threshold && ros::ok()) {
93  readEndEffectorPosition();
94  positionErrorVector = desiredPositionVector - endEffectorPositionVector;
95  desiredEEVelocity = pGain * positionErrorVector;
96  ros::spinOnce();
97  switch (avoidanceMode) {
98  case Flacco:
99  ROS_INFO("Flacco selected");
100  ros::shutdown();
101  break;
102  case QP:
103  ROS_INFO("QP selected");
104  ros::shutdown();
105  break;
106  default:
107  jointVelocityController.sendVelocities(EEVelocityToQDot(desiredEEVelocity));
108  }
109  rate.sleep();
110  }
111  jointVelocityController.sendVelocities(Eigen::VectorXd::Constant(7, 0.0));
112 }
113 
114 void on_shutdown(int sig) {
115  CartesianPositionController endController;
116  endController.jointVelocityController.sendVelocities(Eigen::VectorXd::Constant(7, 0.0));
117  ros::shutdown();
118 }
